text: Krasimira Tocheva (born 28 July 1967) is a Bulgarian rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Bulgaria Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers from Sofia
